          o openSUSE 11.1
          o openSUSE 11.0
          o SUSE Linux Enterprise 11
          o SUSE Linux Enterprise 10
          o openSUSE Factory

    * Red Hat
          o Fedora 12
          o Fedora 11
          o Fedora 10
          o Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5
          o CentOS 5

    * Mandriva Linux
          o Mandriva 2010
          o Mandriva 2009.1
          o Mandriva 2009

